On 20/10/06, Marcus Meissner <meissner@suse.de> wrote:
> Randomizes -pie compiled binaries from PAGE_SIZE up to
> ELF_ET_DYN_BASE.
>
> 0 -> PAGE_SIZE is excluded to allow NULL ptr accesses
> to fail.
>
> Signed-off-by: Marcus Meissner <meissner@suse.de>
>
> ----
>  binfmt_elf.c |    8 +++++++-
